<template><header class="header"><a href="/" class="header__logo"><span class="header__logo-mark">M</span>Design System</a><nav class="header__nav"><a href="/" class="header__nav-link">Foundations</a><a href="/documentation/select.html" class="header__nav-link is-active">Components</a></nav></header><div class="layout"><nav class="layout__nav"><div class="nav"><section class="nav__section"><span class="nav__section-title">Components</span><ul class="nav__list"><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/button.html" class="nav__link">Button</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/toggle.html" class="nav__link">Toggle</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/checkbox.html" class="nav__link">Checkbox</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/input.html" class="nav__link">Input</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/select.html" class="nav__link is-active">Select</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/radio.html" class="nav__link">Radio</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/textarea.html" class="nav__link">Textarea</a></li><li class="nav__item"><a href="/documentation/tabs.html" class="nav__link">Tabs</a></li></ul></section></div></nav><main class="layout__content"><article class="content"><span class="content__eyebrow">Components</span><h1>Select</h1><p class="content__lead">Single-option picker with optional icon/flag, two sizes, custom dropdown, and disabled state.</p><h2 id="purpose" class="comp-section-h2">Purpose &amp; when to use</h2><ul><li>Use for selecting one item from a predefined list.</li><li>Use text input when free typing is needed.</li></ul><h2 id="anatomy" class="comp-section-h2">Anatomy &amp; sizing</h2><div class="comp-demo"><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Small</span><Select v-model="smallValue" size="small" :options="options" placeholder="Select option..." /></div><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Medium</span><Select v-model="mediumValue" size="medium" :options="options" placeholder="Select option..." /></div></div><table class="props-table"><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Token</th><th>Value</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>small padding</td><td><code>--marks-spacing-8/16</code></td><td>8px 16px (right 40)</td></tr><tr><td>small radius</td><td><code>--marks-radius-8</code></td><td>8px</td></tr><tr><td>medium padding</td><td><code>--marks-spacing-20</code></td><td>top/bottom 14, left 20, right 40</td></tr><tr><td>medium radius</td><td><code>--marks-radius-12</code></td><td>12px</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="variants" class="comp-section-h2">Variants &amp; all states</h2><div class="comp-demo"><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Default</span><Select v-model="defaultValue" :options="options" /></div><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Disabled</span><Select v-model="defaultValue" :options="options" :disabled="true" /></div></div><h2 id="behavior" class="comp-section-h2">Behavior rules</h2><ul><li>Click toggles dropdown when enabled.</li><li>Select emits <code>update:modelValue</code> and <code>change</code>.</li><li>Outside click closes dropdown.</li></ul><h2 id="content" class="comp-section-h2">Content rules</h2><ul><li>Use concise option labels.</li><li>Placeholder should guide action ("Select country").</li></ul><h2 id="accessibility" class="comp-section-h2">Accessibility</h2><ul><li>Uses button semantics for trigger and focus states.</li><li>Disabled state uses native <code>disabled</code> attribute.</li></ul><h2 id="examples" class="comp-section-h2">Examples &amp; anti-patterns</h2><div class="comp-demo"><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label">Do</span><Select v-model="exampleValue" :options="options" placeholder="Select plan" /></div><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;"><span class="comp-demo__group-label" style="color:#FD3860;">Don't</span><Select v-model="exampleValue" :options="[{label:'Very very very very long option label that truncates badly',value:'1'}]" placeholder="Pick" /></div></div><h2 id="api" class="comp-section-h2">API / Props</h2><table class="props-table"><thead><tr><th>Name</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>modelValue</code></td><td>String|Number</td><td>null</td><td>Selected value.</td></tr><tr><td><code>size</code></td><td>'small'|'medium'</td><td>'medium'</td><td>Control size.</td></tr><tr><td><code>placeholder</code></td><td>String</td><td>'Select option...'</td><td>Displayed when no value.</td></tr><tr><td><code>options</code></td><td>Array</td><td>[]</td><td>Dropdown options.</td></tr><tr><td><code>leftIcon</code></td><td>Object|String</td><td>null</td><td>Optional left icon.</td></tr><tr><td><code>flag</code></td><td>String</td><td>null</td><td>Optional flag image URL.</td></tr><tr><td><code>flagAlt</code></td><td>String</td><td>''</td><td>Flag alt text.</td></tr><tr><td><code>disabled</code></td><td>Boolean</td><td>false</td><td>Disabled state.</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="theming" class="comp-section-h2">Theming &amp; dark mode</h2><div class="comp-demo dark-preview"><div class="comp-demo__group" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;"><Select v-model="themeValue" :options="options" /></div></div></article></main><aside class="layout__aside"><div class="aside"><div class="aside__block aside__block--code"><div class="code-pane is-active"><pre><span class="token-tag">&lt;Select</span> <span class="token-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="token-string">"value"</span> <span class="token-attr">:options</span>=<span class="token-string">"options"</span> <span class="token-tag">/&gt;</span></pre></div></div></div></aside></div></template>
<script>export default{name:'SelectDocPage',data(){return{smallValue:null,mediumValue:null,defaultValue:null,exampleValue:null,themeValue:null,options:[{label:'Standard',value:'standard'},{label:'Premium',value:'premium'},{label:'Enterprise',value:'enterprise'}]}}}</script>
